    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-main-workflow-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\ude80 AI Lead Management System",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        50,
        50
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 1200,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "# \ud83d\ude80 AI Lead Management System with GoHighLevel CRM & Google Drive\n\n**Automated Email Processing** \u2192 **Web Research & Scraping** \u2192 **AI Analysis** \u2192 **CRM Integration** \u2192 **File Storage** \u2192 **Priority Alerts**\n\nThis workflow automatically processes incoming emails, researches leads, stores analysis in Google Drive, and manages your entire sales pipeline in GoHighLevel CRM."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-email-processing-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udce7 Email Processing Pipeline",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        80,
        250
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 4,
        "width": 400,
        "height": 180,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udce7 Email Processing Pipeline\n\n**Gmail Trigger**: Monitors inbox for new emails\n- Polls every minute for new messages\n- Filters out spam and trash\n- Processes all incoming inquiries\n\n**Smart Switch**: Routes emails by content\n- Lead inquiries \u2192 CRM processing\n- Partnerships \u2192 Specialized handling\n- Other emails \u2192 General processing"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-crm-integration-001",
      "name": "\ud83c\udfe2 GoHighLevel CRM Integration",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        480,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 450,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "## \ud83c\udfe2 GoHighLevel CRM Integration\n\n**CRM Agent**: AI-powered lead processing\n- Extracts contact details from emails\n- Formats data for CRM entry\n- Determines lead classification\n\n**Add Contact**: Creates new leads in GHL\n- Auto-fills contact information\n- Adds custom fields and tags\n- Sets initial lead status\n\n**Opportunity Creation**: Builds sales pipeline\n- Creates opportunities with monetary value\n- Sets appropriate pipeline stage\n- Links to contact record"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-research-scraping-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udd0d Web Research & Scraping",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        880,
        50
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 6,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 220,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udd0d Web Research & Scraping\n\n**Website Discovery**: Finds company websites\n- Uses Hunter.io API for domain research\n- Extracts organization details\n- Identifies primary business website\n\n**Content Scraping**: Extracts website content\n- Scrapes full website content\n- Converts HTML to readable markdown\n- Processes for AI analysis\n\n**LinkedIn Search**: Locates social profiles\n- Searches for company LinkedIn pages\n- Uses ProxyCrawl for reliable scraping\n- Stores profile URLs for reference"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-ai-analysis-001",
      "name": "\ud83e\udd16 AI Analysis Engine",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1450,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 3,
        "width": 420,
        "height": 180,
        "content": "## \ud83e\udd16 AI Analysis Engine\n\n**Lead Summary Agent**: Creates comprehensive profiles\n- Analyzes company overview and industry\n- Calculates business potential and ROI\n- Identifies pain points and solution fit\n- Recommends sales approach strategies\n\n**Uses GPT-4o Latest** for high-quality analysis\n- Temperature: 0.3 for balanced creativity\n- Max tokens: 2000 for detailed reports\n- Structured output for CRM integration"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-google-drive-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udcc1 Google Drive File Management",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1680,
        50
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 2,
        "width": 450,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udcc1 Google Drive File Management\n\n**Folder Creation**: Organizes lead files\n- Creates folders by company and date\n- Stores in designated parent directory\n- Maintains organized file structure\n\n**Analysis Storage**: Saves comprehensive reports\n- Lead analysis as readable text files\n- Email data as structured JSON\n- Timestamps for tracking and auditing\n\n**CRM Integration**: Links files to records\n- Stores Drive file IDs in GoHighLevel\n- Creates accessible file references\n- Enables team collaboration"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-email-automation-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udcec Email Automation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        480,
        350
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 1,
        "width": 420,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udcec Email Automation\n\n**Main AI Agent**: Intelligent email processing\n- Categorizes emails (lead, partnership, support)\n- Assigns priority levels (high, medium, low)\n- Determines lead scores (hot, warm, cold)\n- Suggests response strategies\n\n**Structured Parser**: Formats AI output\n- Ensures consistent data structure\n- Validates CRM field requirements\n- Provides automation trigger recommendations\n\n**Auto-Response**: Sends acknowledgments\n- Professional automated replies\n- Sets expectations for follow-up\n- Confirms CRM integration status"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-priority-alerts-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udea8 Priority Alert System",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1200,
        350
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 1,
        "width": 400,
        "height": 180,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udea8 Priority Alert System\n\n**Smart Switch**: Identifies high-priority leads\n- Checks priority level = \"high\"\n- Monitors lead score = \"hot\"\n- Triggers immediate notifications\n\n**Instant Alerts**: Notifies sales team\n- Sends detailed lead information\n- Includes AI analysis summary\n- Provides CRM record links\n- Contains Google Drive file references\n- Demands immediate follow-up action"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-setup-instructions-001",
      "name": "\u2699\ufe0f Setup Instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        50,
        600
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 600,
        "height": 300,
        "content": "## \u2699\ufe0f Setup Instructions\n\n### Required API Credentials:\n- **OpenAI API**: For AI analysis (GPT-4o)\n- **Gmail OAuth2**: For email monitoring\n- **GoHighLevel API**: For CRM operations\n- **Hunter.io API**: For domain research\n- **ProxyCrawl API**: For web scraping\n- **Google Drive OAuth2**: For file storage\n\n### GoHighLevel Configuration:\n- Set up custom fields for analysis data\n- Create pipeline for lead opportunities\n- Configure tags for lead categorization\n- Set monetary values for opportunities\n\n### Google Drive Setup:\n- Create parent folder for lead storage\n- Set proper sharing permissions\n- Configure OAuth2 access"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-workflow-benefits-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udca1 Workflow Benefits",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        700,
        600
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 3,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 300,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udca1 Workflow Benefits\n\n### \ud83c\udfaf Lead Management:\n- **100% Automation**: Zero manual email processing\n- **Instant CRM Entry**: Immediate lead capture\n- **AI-Powered Analysis**: Deep prospect insights\n- **Research Integration**: Complete company profiles\n\n### \ud83d\udcca Business Impact:\n- **Faster Response Times**: Immediate acknowledgments\n- **Better Lead Scoring**: AI-driven prioritization\n- **Complete Documentation**: All data stored and linked\n- **Sales Team Efficiency**: Pre-qualified opportunities\n\n### \ud83d\udd04 Scalability:\n- **Handles High Volume**: Processes unlimited emails\n- **Consistent Quality**: Standardized lead processing\n- **Team Collaboration**: Shared files and CRM access\n- **Growth Ready**: Scales with your business"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-customization-001",
      "name": "\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Customization Options",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1250,
        600
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 4,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 300,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Customization Options\n\n### \ud83c\udfa8 Email Routing:\n- Modify switch conditions for your keywords\n- Add new categories (support, sales, etc.)\n- Customize priority scoring rules\n\n### \ud83e\udd16 AI Prompts:\n- Adapt analysis prompts for your industry\n- Modify lead scoring criteria\n- Customize response templates\n\n### \ud83c\udfe2 CRM Fields:\n- Add custom fields to GoHighLevel\n- Modify pipeline stages and values\n- Customize tag categories\n\n### \ud83d\udcc1 File Organization:\n- Change folder naming conventions\n- Modify file formats and templates\n- Add additional metadata fields\n\n### \ud83d\udce7 Notifications:\n- Customize alert recipients\n- Modify notification templates\n- Add Slack/Teams integration"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    }
  ],
